DimensionsObjectDetails
public class TransitionRoleDetails
extends java.lang.Object
implements DimensionsObjectDetails

Represents the details of a Dimensions role that is authorized to perform a lifecycle state transition.

TransitionRoleDetails

public TransitionRoleDetails(java.lang.String roleName,
                             boolean optional,
                             boolean pending)
Constructs an initialized object.

Parameters:
roleName - name of the role
optional - the OPTIONAL flag for the role. True: actioning an object to the 'From State' does not require the existence of a user holding the role (otherwise, false).
pending - the PENDING flag for the role. True: the object will appear in the Pending List of the role holders when it is actioned to the 'From State'.

getPending(), setPending(boolean), getOptional(), setOptional(boolean)
